TITLE: Episode 33 - Girl Talk With Monica Perez
DESCRIPTION: Maddie and Jessie sit down with Monica Perez from “The Propaganda Report” for some much needed girl talk. Girl talk included impeachment, labor law history, coronavirus conspiracies and so much more. You know, just your basic girly stuff.
